WEBVTT

00:37.360 --> 00:39.080
How did you end up in such a sorry state?

00:43.440 --> 00:44.520
Fate toys with us all.

00:45.520 --> 00:46.800
Who could have foreseen this?

00:49.240 --> 00:50.440
But duty bound me.

00:51.880 --> 00:52.920
I did all that I could.

00:55.400 --> 00:56.640
As Military Administrator,

00:58.400 --> 01:00.000
you were charged with overseeing the army.

01:00.600 --> 01:02.560
Yet the rebel Sui Yuanhuai

01:02.640 --> 01:04.040
has slipped away time and again.

01:04.680 --> 01:05.840
You cannot evade responsibility.

01:07.840 --> 01:09.400
This was indeed my failure in duty.

01:10.240 --> 01:13.120
I have already reported it
in a memorial to His Majesty

01:13.960 --> 01:15.240
and asked to be punished.

01:24.840 --> 01:26.560
You served under General He for years.

01:27.320 --> 01:29.600
You must know Li Bai's poem
South of the City Walls.

01:30.600 --> 01:33.280
The soldiers lie scattered in the weeds
While the generals bear empty titles

01:34.360 --> 01:35.680
For the sake of so-called legitimacy,

01:36.480 --> 01:38.720
countless lives have been sacrificed.

01:38.800 --> 01:39.680
What cruelty.

01:40.640 --> 01:41.840
You call it a failure in duty.

01:41.920 --> 01:44.640
Do you know how many soldiers' sacrifices
have come to nothing?

01:44.720 --> 01:46.480
How many civilians are trapped in misery?

01:47.640 --> 01:49.480
I carry the shame deeply.

01:54.040 --> 01:55.560
As the eldest grandson of the Lis,

01:56.920 --> 01:58.080
I alone shall bear

01:59.280 --> 02:00.880
the infamy for generations.

02:04.600 --> 02:06.160
A senseless fabricated war.

02:07.560 --> 02:09.240
Fallen soldiers into restless ghosts.

02:09.320 --> 02:10.639
Can you shoulder that weight?

02:13.000 --> 02:13.840
Lord Li,

02:15.200 --> 02:16.680
let me remind you of something.

02:17.480 --> 02:19.760
Do not forget why you entered
official service.

02:36.960 --> 02:38.640
What did Marquis Wu'an say?

02:38.720 --> 02:40.000
Xie Zheng…

02:43.800 --> 02:45.040
He likely knows everything now.

04:13.160 --> 04:17.920
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

04:20.720 --> 04:23.560
SESAME FLATBREAD

04:26.960 --> 04:29.720
What sins did the Liu family commit
to suffer this?

04:29.800 --> 04:31.920
Their whole household was slaughtered.

04:32.000 --> 04:32.840
WANTED, PUBLIC NOTICE

04:32.920 --> 04:34.360
The bandits are ruthless.

04:34.920 --> 04:36.720
What is one Liu household?

04:36.800 --> 04:38.840
The entire town of Lin'an was wiped out.

04:39.760 --> 04:42.520
No wonder Marquis Wu'an
went after Qingfeng Stronghold.

04:43.480 --> 04:45.520
He is truly ridding the people of evil.

04:45.600 --> 04:46.520
That is right.

04:46.600 --> 04:49.120
Look at this young woman.
Pretty as a flower.

04:49.200 --> 04:52.240
Yet she calls herself a bandit?
Leader of Qingfeng Stronghold?

04:52.320 --> 04:54.200
-Five stuffed flatbreads.
-All right.

04:54.280 --> 04:56.040
-Bah.
-Here you go.

05:04.920 --> 05:06.120
Watch out where you are going.

05:37.920 --> 05:39.280
Sui Yuanqing…

05:43.800 --> 05:45.080
You heartless bastard.

05:45.920 --> 05:47.600
Where the hell did you disappear to?

05:50.680 --> 05:52.840
The authorities are hunting me.

05:53.800 --> 05:55.760
The outlaws are hunting me.

05:56.800 --> 06:00.200
Even the deaths of 13 in the Liu household
have been pinned on me.

06:01.560 --> 06:02.880
Now I am being chased

06:03.400 --> 06:05.640
like a stray dog.

06:05.720 --> 06:06.720
And you…

06:07.520 --> 06:09.000
Not even a trace of you.

06:35.880 --> 06:37.880
Is that not the official from Lin'an?

06:37.960 --> 06:39.240
What is he doing here?

07:12.280 --> 07:15.200
SOVEREIGN AND EFFICACIOUS

07:21.640 --> 07:23.960
Have some hot tea
to ward off the cold, Your Highness.

07:28.160 --> 07:30.080
We are not far from the capital now.

07:30.600 --> 07:32.960
Once we arrive there, you will be safe.

07:35.800 --> 07:36.920
Qi Min!

07:37.520 --> 07:39.120
Get out here!

07:46.480 --> 07:47.680
Again?

07:48.200 --> 07:51.440
His nose is sharper than a hunting dog.
He truly is impossible to shake.

08:33.640 --> 08:35.280
I will kill you, you wretched bastard,

08:35.880 --> 08:38.000
then go join Father
and Mother in the afterlife.

08:39.640 --> 08:42.679
You stole my brother's name
and lived under it for over a decade.

08:44.440 --> 08:46.920
Surely you have nothing left to say.

08:48.840 --> 08:49.680
Yuanqing.

08:51.320 --> 08:53.680
Do not call me that.

09:04.800 --> 09:05.800
Yuanqing.

09:06.520 --> 09:07.680
If you resent me,

09:09.040 --> 09:10.640
then please accept my apology.

09:10.720 --> 09:12.560
Believe it or not,

09:13.520 --> 09:15.320
I never meant to harm you.

09:19.040 --> 09:20.760
Never meant to harm me?

09:21.360 --> 09:22.400
Then what about my mother?

09:23.040 --> 09:24.760
What wrong did she ever do to you?

09:24.840 --> 09:27.880
Answer me. Answer me!

09:50.920 --> 09:52.520
Is this what you mean…

09:54.640 --> 09:56.480
by never meaning to harm me?

09:58.840 --> 09:59.760
Yuanqing.

10:00.680 --> 10:02.080
I warned you long ago

10:02.880 --> 10:04.600
not to be so arrogant.

10:05.640 --> 10:07.720
Now I will finish the saying for you.

10:09.320 --> 10:12.440
Those who act so meet a violent end.

10:29.280 --> 10:30.160
I was a fool.

10:30.920 --> 10:32.680
I always treated you as my own brother.

10:33.680 --> 10:35.560
I could not even bring myself to kill you.

10:41.040 --> 10:43.480
Your family owes me a debt!

10:44.000 --> 10:46.520
The entire household of Prince Changxin
deserves to die!

10:49.720 --> 10:51.520
Why is it you grew strong and capable,

10:52.040 --> 10:53.960
while I became this half man, half ghost?

10:54.040 --> 10:55.800
Why could you train in martial arts,

10:55.880 --> 10:57.600
ride horses, shoot arrows,

10:58.120 --> 11:00.880
while I was left with sickness,
forced to swallow medicine day after day?

11:02.120 --> 11:05.760
The pain in my heart
and the wounds on my body

11:05.840 --> 11:08.840
were all caused by Prince Changxin
and Wei Yan.

11:09.680 --> 11:11.520
My father. My mother.

11:12.040 --> 11:14.520
I must avenge them.

11:14.600 --> 11:18.240
Every one of you
will meet a miserable end!

11:22.080 --> 11:24.440
You speak as if you are righteous.

11:26.280 --> 11:28.800
Yet my mother never treated you poorly.

11:29.720 --> 11:31.880
It was the Crown Princess
who killed my brother.

11:32.640 --> 11:35.360
My mother raised you
for more than ten years.

11:36.040 --> 11:37.800
You stole my brother's place.

11:38.520 --> 11:41.520
How could you bring yourself to kill her?

11:44.960 --> 11:47.280
Because my heart died long ago.

11:48.480 --> 11:51.080
Of course I could do it.

11:55.960 --> 11:58.000
We must go, Your Highness.
This place is not safe.

12:31.720 --> 12:32.800
Sui Yuanqing,

12:33.920 --> 12:35.280
have you forgotten

12:36.040 --> 12:38.000
what I once taught you?

12:38.920 --> 12:40.880
Those who show mercy

12:42.600 --> 12:45.640
have no place in a land of killing.

12:46.160 --> 12:47.880
And do not even dream

12:49.160 --> 12:51.200
of ruling this world.

14:12.320 --> 14:14.000
Your Highness.
I came as quickly as I could.

14:16.720 --> 14:18.560
Why not come after I'm dead instead?

14:20.840 --> 14:22.720
It was your Li clan who sent word to me,

14:22.800 --> 14:24.440
saying everything had been arranged.

14:24.520 --> 14:27.000
Yet what awaited me along the way?

14:27.680 --> 14:29.920
Xie Zheng's personal guards

14:30.440 --> 14:32.520
and that madman Sui Yuanqing.

14:34.400 --> 14:36.040
This was indeed my failing.

14:36.920 --> 14:38.160
Punish me as you see fit.

14:40.560 --> 14:41.880
I know you do not like me.

14:42.920 --> 14:44.520
Protecting me, saving me…

14:45.040 --> 14:47.080
You only do it
because your grandfather commands it.

14:48.120 --> 14:49.800
But now that you have boarded this ship,

14:49.880 --> 14:51.880
there is no turning back.

14:53.280 --> 14:55.280
Only by seeing me safely into the capital

14:56.120 --> 14:58.200
will your Li clan
have even the slightest chance.

14:58.720 --> 15:00.440
All those years of planning
won't be wasted.

15:03.240 --> 15:06.120
Otherwise,
I will drag us all down together.

15:06.880 --> 15:09.320
Your Li clan will be wiped out,

15:09.400 --> 15:12.160
and Wei Yan will sit in power
for decades to come.

15:12.960 --> 15:14.480
The people will suffer endlessly.

15:19.920 --> 15:22.280
I have heard you care deeply
for common folks.

15:23.400 --> 15:25.440
Surely you don't wish
for war and bloodshed to rise again.

15:29.080 --> 15:29.960
I will

15:31.400 --> 15:32.600
do everything in my power.

15:34.640 --> 15:35.480
One more thing.

15:36.480 --> 15:38.240
I do not care how you do it.

15:39.240 --> 15:41.160
Kill Yu Bao'er,

15:41.240 --> 15:43.320
and bring Yu Qianqian to me
without a single scratch.

15:44.800 --> 15:45.680
Your Highness.

15:47.000 --> 15:49.400
I heard Yu Bao'er is your only bloodline.

15:50.280 --> 15:51.200
I do not acknowledge him.

15:51.720 --> 15:53.320
That bloodline would only be my ruin.

15:55.120 --> 15:56.160
One worthless life

15:56.800 --> 15:58.360
against the fate of the Li clan.

15:58.440 --> 16:01.240
You know well enough which matters more.

16:18.800 --> 16:20.680
‎SOVEREIGN AND EFFICACIOUS

16:23.200 --> 16:25.040
If you fail to find the person I want,

16:25.560 --> 16:27.320
then the alliance between me and the Lis

16:27.840 --> 16:29.120
ends here.

16:38.480 --> 16:40.800
He repaid kindness with blood.
Brother against brother.

16:41.560 --> 16:42.880
Now he hunts his own son.

16:44.280 --> 16:45.880
How can a man with no loyalty or honor

16:47.000 --> 16:48.360
rule as emperor?

16:50.840 --> 16:52.200
If he ever takes the throne,

16:52.960 --> 16:54.360
he will be no wise ruler.

16:57.600 --> 16:58.560
Grandfather,

16:59.920 --> 17:01.240
you truly were wrong.

17:48.800 --> 17:50.160
So you are not dead yet.

17:56.080 --> 17:57.160
Kill me.

17:58.800 --> 18:00.400
Take your revenge.

18:04.120 --> 18:05.440
Fine.

18:10.040 --> 18:11.200
Sui Yuanqing.

18:13.680 --> 18:14.880
Before you die…

18:18.320 --> 18:19.600
I want to ask you something.

18:24.040 --> 18:26.480
Did you ever feel
the slightest love for me?

18:35.680 --> 18:37.520
In my life,

18:38.400 --> 18:39.920
I have deceived countless people.

18:42.480 --> 18:43.880
Now that I am close to dying…

18:46.120 --> 18:47.320
I suppose

18:48.280 --> 18:49.920
I should spin some comforting lies

18:51.800 --> 18:53.280
so you would risk your life for me.

18:55.280 --> 18:57.560
But strangely enough…

19:00.960 --> 19:03.480
right now, I do not want to lie to you.

19:08.000 --> 19:09.240
Not even a little.

19:11.320 --> 19:13.720
I never felt the slightest love for you.

19:23.320 --> 19:25.120
With the kind of man you are,

19:27.000 --> 19:28.480
that is probably for the best.

19:36.560 --> 19:37.880
Without you around…

19:40.840 --> 19:42.480
my days ahead…

19:45.440 --> 19:47.400
will be freer than ever.

20:02.200 --> 20:04.200
If you manage to survive,

20:04.960 --> 20:05.800
take this

20:07.520 --> 20:09.360
and go find Fan Changyu.

20:14.360 --> 20:15.200
What is it?

20:19.440 --> 20:21.400
You were with me once.

20:21.920 --> 20:24.120
So I will leave you a way to survive.

20:25.600 --> 20:28.880
Qi Min wants the whole world to suffer.

20:29.680 --> 20:31.080
I, Sui Yuanqing,

20:32.280 --> 20:34.680
only want him to suffer alone.

20:36.280 --> 20:38.080
Why would she believe me?

21:02.600 --> 21:04.640
This is the proper token from me…

21:08.480 --> 21:10.320
to prove your loyalty.

21:40.560 --> 21:42.320
Sui Yuanqing!

21:51.680 --> 21:53.880
THREE DAYS LATER

21:53.960 --> 21:56.800
Your Majesty,
I have a memorial to present.

21:56.880 --> 22:00.080
Chancellor Wei's lax discipline
has bred near defiance.

22:00.160 --> 22:02.200
Such an offense
should be punished severely.

22:07.960 --> 22:10.600
Grand Tutor Li understands my mind.
Speak freely.

22:10.680 --> 22:12.040
Your Majesty,

22:12.120 --> 22:15.440
Marquis Wu'an is Chancellor Wei's nephew,
brought up under his wing.

22:15.520 --> 22:16.440
He dared cut off the ear

22:16.520 --> 22:19.800
of the imperial envoy, Eunuch Li,
before the assembled army.

22:20.320 --> 22:22.920
Such arrogance and tyranny
is nothing short of treason.

22:23.000 --> 22:26.920
By the law, he should be executed
to serve as a warning to others.

22:30.200 --> 22:32.400
Grand Tutor Li speaks frankly.

22:34.240 --> 22:35.960
Chancellor Wei, what say you?

22:36.880 --> 22:38.400
In my view,

22:39.240 --> 22:40.560
Eunuch Li kept insisting

22:40.640 --> 22:44.400
that Marquis Wu'an intended to rebel.

22:44.480 --> 22:46.280
So I believe

22:46.360 --> 22:49.760
the marquis simply acted
in anger and lost control.

22:51.320 --> 22:55.280
After all, not everyone in this world
can be as gentle and composed

22:55.360 --> 22:58.000
as Grand Tutor Li's grandson,
Military Administrator Li Huai'an.

22:58.080 --> 23:00.800
Even when Your Majesty
suddenly changed your decision

23:00.880 --> 23:03.360
and betrothed the Grand Princess
to another man,

23:03.440 --> 23:06.120
he accepted it with admirable composure.

23:11.440 --> 23:14.040
Chancellor Wei makes a fair point.

23:15.040 --> 23:16.760
Military men

23:16.840 --> 23:18.920
do tend to act a little roughly.

23:25.120 --> 23:26.040
Chancellor Wei,

23:26.920 --> 23:30.920
half of He Jingyuan's command has fallen
into the hands of a mere village woman.

23:31.520 --> 23:34.840
Captain Fan Changyu cannot even read
military maps or strategy manuals.

23:35.440 --> 23:37.400
Yet through your private maneuvering,

23:37.480 --> 23:39.200
she is now
a supervising commander of Jizhou.

23:39.280 --> 23:41.680
The command office
is now in utter disarray.

23:41.760 --> 23:43.920
May I ask, where is the army's discipline?

23:44.000 --> 23:45.840
Where is the law of the realm?

23:45.920 --> 23:47.440
Such a thing has truly happened?

23:50.760 --> 23:51.600
Your Majesty,

23:51.680 --> 23:55.520
both Marquis Wu'an and Captain Fan
have rendered great service.

23:55.600 --> 23:58.320
Merit and fault must be judged separately.

23:58.400 --> 24:00.760
What does Your Majesty think?

24:03.520 --> 24:05.000
Report!

24:06.360 --> 24:07.280
Your Majesty!

24:07.360 --> 24:09.680
An 800-li express dispatch
has arrived from Jizhou.

24:09.760 --> 24:10.600
-Bring it.
-Yes.

24:20.040 --> 24:21.320
Excellent.

24:21.960 --> 24:24.000
Marquis Wu'an joined forces
with Captain Fan

24:24.520 --> 24:25.960
and has slain the rebel Sui Yuanhuai.

24:26.960 --> 24:29.800
Prince Changxin and his two sons are dead.

24:29.880 --> 24:33.280
The Sui line is extinguished.
The Chongzhou rebel army is no more.

24:33.360 --> 24:34.440
Excellent!

24:40.080 --> 24:44.040
A general and his commander working
in harmony to defeat the enemy leader.

24:44.720 --> 24:47.040
This is a great fortune for me

24:47.120 --> 24:49.240
and a blessing for Dayin.

24:52.880 --> 24:57.240
The world is like a chessboard.
Every move brings a new game.

24:57.880 --> 25:00.960
Since Marquis Wu'an and Captain Fan
have won such remarkable victories,

25:01.560 --> 25:04.800
then I shall reward them.
And I shall reward them generously.

25:05.480 --> 25:07.200
Your Majesty is wise.

25:10.000 --> 25:11.240
Your Majesty is wise.

25:13.160 --> 25:16.240
JIZHOU YAMEN

25:16.320 --> 25:19.320
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

25:28.520 --> 25:29.520
My lord,

25:29.600 --> 25:31.360
the Grand Princess leaves
for the capital tomorrow.

25:31.880 --> 25:33.680
Captain Fan has arranged
a farewell banquet.

25:34.880 --> 25:35.880
Will you attend?

25:53.320 --> 25:54.160
Also,

25:54.240 --> 25:57.120
at dawn, Marquis Wu'an's men
will escort the Grand Princess.

26:12.720 --> 26:14.160
I am too ashamed to face them.

26:27.600 --> 26:28.720
-Come on!
-Come on!

26:28.800 --> 26:30.680
Pour it up!

26:31.200 --> 26:32.320
HALL OF LETTERS

26:50.440 --> 26:51.280
-Thirty-two!
-Twenty-two!

26:51.360 --> 26:52.600
‎Cheers.

26:53.640 --> 26:55.040
‎Drink up.

26:59.320 --> 27:01.760
Everyone's already drunk
out of their minds.

27:01.840 --> 27:03.760
Where is Military Administrator Li?

27:04.760 --> 27:06.560
He caught a chill.

27:06.640 --> 27:07.920
He will not make it tonight.

27:10.600 --> 27:11.520
Everyone,

27:12.520 --> 27:15.440
I cannot hold my drink.
After this cup, I will take my leave.

27:30.560 --> 27:32.200
Safe travels, Your Highness.

27:42.920 --> 27:43.840
Sit.

27:49.000 --> 27:50.480
Her Highness returns
to the capital tomorrow.

27:51.400 --> 27:53.600
If anyone has something to say,

27:53.680 --> 27:55.440
tonight is the night.

27:57.240 --> 27:58.880
-I will go!
-Sit down.

27:58.960 --> 27:59.800
All right.

28:03.520 --> 28:04.560
Go on then.

28:06.840 --> 28:07.960
Where is he going?

28:09.400 --> 28:11.000
Is he actually… He really went?

28:12.400 --> 28:14.520
Your Highness! Your Highness, please wait.

28:15.760 --> 28:17.760
-Your Highness.
-Her Highness does not wish to see you.

28:17.840 --> 28:19.560
-I only wish to ask a few questions.
-Move aside.

28:21.320 --> 28:23.920
I doubt Your Highness would return
with doubts left unresolved.

28:31.240 --> 28:32.280
Leave us, Jianjia.

28:39.960 --> 28:40.800
Allow me.

28:47.720 --> 28:48.600
Your Highness.

28:49.960 --> 28:53.200
Why have you suddenly decided
to return to the capital?

28:54.760 --> 28:56.840
I have spent more than five months
in the northwest.

28:57.840 --> 28:59.400
I am weary in both body and mind.

29:00.680 --> 29:02.040
I've come to my senses.

29:03.400 --> 29:05.080
I won't cling to what's futile.

29:07.600 --> 29:10.360
Surely you must feel
greatly relieved, Headmaster.

29:13.240 --> 29:14.800
Since you have reached such clarity,

29:15.640 --> 29:17.480
I ought to offer my congratulations.

29:18.440 --> 29:19.520
But there are words

29:20.920 --> 29:23.760
I have kept in my heart for a long time.
I have long wished to share them.

29:25.200 --> 29:26.640
Yet the rules of my clan are strict.

29:26.720 --> 29:27.640
I dared not overstep.

29:30.520 --> 29:31.840
So a few days ago,

29:33.080 --> 29:34.360
I returned to Hejian

29:36.040 --> 29:37.720
and knelt in the ancestral hall
for three days.

29:39.720 --> 29:41.560
Only after receiving
the clan elder's pardon

29:42.880 --> 29:44.000
did I dare come here

29:45.200 --> 29:46.840
to speak my heart before Your Highness.

29:50.240 --> 29:51.280
Go on.

29:54.160 --> 29:55.000
Changyu.

29:57.360 --> 29:58.480
-I…
-Easy there.

29:58.560 --> 30:00.760
I need to drink a few cups with you alone.

30:01.480 --> 30:03.120
Do you still have wine?

30:04.840 --> 30:07.120
Let me… Let me speak honestly.

30:08.320 --> 30:11.880
I, Jin Yuanbao, have never
respected anyone, but I respect you.

30:12.840 --> 30:14.720
Before I met you,

30:14.800 --> 30:16.600
I never believed

30:16.680 --> 30:19.760
a woman with such thin arms and legs

30:19.840 --> 30:21.560
could fight on a battlefield.

30:22.280 --> 30:25.320
-With a build like yours?
-Never heard of it.

30:25.400 --> 30:26.240
But Changyu can.

30:26.320 --> 30:28.560
That is why I respect you.

30:28.640 --> 30:31.320
-All of us respect you.
-Come on.

30:36.240 --> 30:37.120
Come.

30:38.160 --> 30:40.120
Let's all toast to Captain Fan. Come on.

30:40.200 --> 30:41.400
-Come.
-Folks.

30:41.480 --> 30:42.760
-Pour the wine.
-Fill the cups!

30:43.440 --> 30:45.680
My wife cannot hold her drink.
I will drink for her.

30:47.920 --> 30:49.480
Wife? What wife?

30:50.160 --> 30:52.320
She is the head of your household.

30:53.040 --> 30:54.880
Everyone in Lin'an knows that.

30:54.960 --> 30:56.840
You are the Fan family's
live-in son-in-law.

30:56.920 --> 30:59.880
Once you marry in, you listen
to the head of the house. Right?

30:59.960 --> 31:00.800
That is right.

31:00.880 --> 31:03.480
You walk around these days all dignified.

31:03.560 --> 31:06.320
Yes, yes, Marquis Wu'an.

31:06.400 --> 31:09.360
But you bowed at the wedding altar.
You cannot deny that.

31:09.440 --> 31:10.760
You cannot deny it.

31:12.920 --> 31:16.200
What nonsense about live-in husbands?
I can drink this myself.

31:30.120 --> 31:32.200
I'm getting old.
I can't recall what we were saying.

31:32.280 --> 31:34.440
Not much of a drinker.
I could barely hold my cup steady.

31:35.400 --> 31:37.200
My wife and I will take our leave.

31:37.280 --> 31:40.000
-Everyone keep drinking.
-Changyu.

31:40.080 --> 31:41.000
Well…

31:42.760 --> 31:43.600
A hundred years ago,

31:43.680 --> 31:44.640
CALMING WAVES PAVILION

31:44.720 --> 31:47.280
the Gongsun clan stood
at the height of its glory.

31:48.800 --> 31:51.440
For generations, the empresses
came from our family.

31:53.280 --> 31:54.720
But great height draws danger.

31:55.480 --> 31:56.920
Our fall was a tragic one.

31:57.440 --> 31:59.160
During the reign of the founding emperor,

32:00.200 --> 32:02.080
a dragon robe was found
inside the Eastern Palace.

32:04.400 --> 32:06.920
Crown Prince Shaoyang was reduced
to a commoner.

32:08.560 --> 32:10.240
Two empresses of the Gongsun family

32:11.120 --> 32:12.560
hanged themselves in the palace.

32:12.640 --> 32:14.000
The entire Gongsun clan

32:15.040 --> 32:16.800
was confiscated and exiled.

32:18.920 --> 32:21.760
Even the plaque above the Imperial Library
at Luyuan Academy

32:21.840 --> 32:23.440
was nearly taken down.

32:25.120 --> 32:26.320
I know of that case.

32:27.360 --> 32:28.560
It was determined later

32:29.320 --> 32:30.640
that the Gongsun case

32:31.920 --> 32:34.200
was a wrongful accusation,
a frame-up by a prince.

32:37.280 --> 32:40.440
In this world, there is no such thing
as a flawless frame-up.

32:41.440 --> 32:44.080
In truth, the emperor on the throne
simply could no longer

32:44.160 --> 32:46.040
tolerate the Gongsun clan.

32:47.600 --> 32:48.720
A surviving branch of our clan

32:49.480 --> 32:51.720
has lingered on at Luyuan Academy
for a hundred years.

32:54.160 --> 32:56.520
The first rule in our clan law was this.

32:57.400 --> 32:58.400
No Gongsun may enter official service.

33:03.240 --> 33:04.240
The truth is,

33:05.840 --> 33:07.960
the day Your Highness arrived
at Luyuan Academy,

33:09.040 --> 33:10.760
I already knew you were a woman.

33:12.360 --> 33:15.080
When we first played the Go chess game
at the Imperial Library,

33:15.600 --> 33:17.080
I realized something else.

33:18.680 --> 33:21.640
The one who broke my position
in the Rain Pavilion was you.

33:23.960 --> 33:24.840
But when I learned

33:27.120 --> 33:29.240
that the woman I had admired for so long

33:30.880 --> 33:32.360
was the Grand Princess,

33:34.000 --> 33:35.680
I felt no joy.

33:38.200 --> 33:39.600
Only the feeling that fate was mocking me.

33:41.680 --> 33:43.880
Then why tell me

33:45.800 --> 33:47.000
all of this now?

33:57.720 --> 33:59.440
I wish to ask for Your Highness's hand.

34:02.360 --> 34:03.200
I have

34:05.600 --> 34:06.840
admired you for a long time.

34:07.600 --> 34:10.080
Tonight, I dare ask Your Highness this.

34:11.280 --> 34:12.360
If one day

34:13.360 --> 34:14.520
I help Jiuheng

34:15.159 --> 34:16.880
bring down Wei Yan and the Li clan,

34:19.040 --> 34:20.120
is Your Highness

34:21.199 --> 34:23.080
willing to live with me in Hejian,

34:23.159 --> 34:24.840
free from the cares of the world?

34:31.679 --> 34:33.080
Your Highness need not worry.

34:33.880 --> 34:36.159
My family has means.
We would live comfortably.

34:36.239 --> 34:37.400
Your Highness would not suffer.

34:38.120 --> 34:41.199
-Though Hejian may not compare to--
-And if I say no?

34:55.159 --> 34:56.120
Then…

35:00.560 --> 35:01.800
I have spoken out of turn.

35:03.320 --> 35:04.640
Please forgive my presumption.

35:19.240 --> 35:20.560
You blockhead.

35:23.400 --> 35:24.400
I will take

35:25.320 --> 35:27.880
the 10,000 volumes
in your family's library

35:28.600 --> 35:29.640
as my bride price.

35:30.640 --> 35:31.560
Do you agree?

35:37.880 --> 35:38.720
Are you hesitating?

35:43.840 --> 35:46.200
Yes. Yes, I agree. I agree to everything.

35:47.520 --> 35:50.320
The Gongsun family has 12 library halls.

35:51.360 --> 35:52.520
May I ask, Your Highness,

35:53.160 --> 35:54.400
which one you want?

35:54.480 --> 35:55.960
All of them.

35:58.480 --> 35:59.480
Good.

36:01.240 --> 36:02.080
Very good.

36:08.160 --> 36:10.280
Let go of me.

36:14.720 --> 36:16.600
Where are you taking me?

36:17.680 --> 36:19.760
You've had too much to drink.
Let's get you to bed.

36:20.360 --> 36:22.320
I am not drunk, Marquis.

36:28.440 --> 36:30.120
That word again. Marquis.

36:31.680 --> 36:33.240
Can you stop calling me that?

36:36.440 --> 36:37.800
Call me anything,

36:38.800 --> 36:40.200
except that.

37:00.800 --> 37:02.240
Yan Zheng.

37:03.480 --> 37:04.800
Your name is Yan Zheng.

37:11.120 --> 37:12.120
From now on,

37:13.240 --> 37:15.520
can I call you Yan Zheng?

37:28.680 --> 37:30.200
Your hand…

37:32.040 --> 37:33.040
Does it hurt?

37:53.200 --> 37:54.040
Changyu.

37:57.560 --> 37:58.520
Kiss me.

38:59.560 --> 39:01.320
If you miss me, write me a letter.

39:02.160 --> 39:03.400
I may not understand it fully, but still.

39:08.560 --> 39:09.560
I should be going.

39:10.200 --> 39:11.040
Safe travels.

39:33.640 --> 39:34.480
I am leaving.

40:01.080 --> 40:02.240
If you hate to part so much,

40:02.760 --> 40:04.480
why did you not see her off yourself?

40:04.560 --> 40:06.960
If I had gone,
I might not have let her leave.

40:12.480 --> 40:15.120
A promise is a promise.
Since I gave you my word, it stands.

40:16.320 --> 40:19.040
Since when did it become my fault
for ruining your chances?

40:21.080 --> 40:22.360
We have made an agreement.

40:22.880 --> 40:25.040
Once everything is settled,
we will return to Hejian

40:25.720 --> 40:27.880
and find a quiet place
to spend the rest of our lives.

40:27.960 --> 40:30.120
But the storm in the capital

40:30.200 --> 40:31.520
can no longer be ignored.

40:33.360 --> 40:35.080
Then it is time to return to the capital

40:35.760 --> 40:36.880
and finish

40:37.400 --> 40:38.520
what must be done.

40:42.520 --> 40:48.280
THE CAPITAL

40:55.000 --> 40:56.400
Not bad, not bad.

40:59.600 --> 41:00.680
Have another drink.

41:01.240 --> 41:02.320
-I want that one.
-Here.

41:02.400 --> 41:03.680
-Drink up.
-All right.

41:06.000 --> 41:08.360
-Do not fuss.
-One more cup.

41:10.440 --> 41:11.280
Mr. Li Huaiqin.

41:13.800 --> 41:16.880
I was wondering why I had not seen Yueli
these past few days.

41:19.360 --> 41:22.240
Turns out someone has been holed up
at Jingque House and refuses to leave.

41:28.880 --> 41:30.600
Wei Xuan,

41:30.680 --> 41:33.000
are you not supposed to be serving
in the northwest?

41:34.880 --> 41:36.440
LI HUAIQIN, LI XING'S YOUNGEST GRANDSON

41:36.520 --> 41:38.880
I heard Marquis Wu'an has returned.

41:40.120 --> 41:42.160
What is this? Stepping aside
to make way for him?

41:51.280 --> 41:52.320
Get out.

41:55.880 --> 41:59.160
Seems the stray can never compare
to the real son of the house.

42:01.720 --> 42:03.600
From the looks of it, Marquis Wu'an

42:03.680 --> 42:05.640
must be Chancellor Wei's
true flesh and blood.

42:07.040 --> 42:08.000
Everyone leave.

42:09.520 --> 42:10.400
Yes.

42:24.840 --> 42:27.080
Say that again.

42:28.040 --> 42:29.360
Why play dumb?

42:29.440 --> 42:31.080
The entire capital is talking about it.

42:31.600 --> 42:33.360
They say the Chancellor
and his wife are at odds.

42:34.880 --> 42:36.920
And that you are not even his son.

42:42.800 --> 42:43.920
Wei Xuan, you dare?

42:46.840 --> 42:47.920
You are just a bastard.

42:48.760 --> 42:51.520
All day, you throw your weight around
on Chancellor Wei's name.

42:51.600 --> 42:53.320
And your mother? She's nothing.

42:53.400 --> 42:56.720
Everyone knows Chancellor Wei's true love
was Lady Qi from the palace.

42:59.360 --> 43:00.640
Li Huaiqin,

43:01.160 --> 43:02.600
you're spewing utter nonsense.

43:02.680 --> 43:05.720
If this were the battlefield,
I would have taken your head already.

43:06.640 --> 43:08.080
I will give you one chance.

43:08.160 --> 43:10.720
Shout three times,
"Li is inferior to Wei,"

43:11.640 --> 43:13.400
and I will spare you today.

43:13.480 --> 43:14.680
Bah!

43:14.760 --> 43:16.560
Who do you think you are, Wei Xuan?

43:16.640 --> 43:17.960
Li inferior to Wei?

43:18.040 --> 43:19.200
Wei is inferior to Xie!

43:22.920 --> 43:23.760
Wei Xuan!

43:29.280 --> 43:31.680
END CREDIT SCENE

44:10.320 --> 44:11.880
Changyu and the Marquis…

44:11.960 --> 44:13.840
-They… They…
-What is it?

44:14.360 --> 44:15.200
Come look for yourself.

44:15.280 --> 44:16.360
Look, look!

44:19.520 --> 44:21.200
-The Marquis…
-What Marquis?

44:21.280 --> 44:22.920
I was just about to curse him out.

44:23.440 --> 44:26.240
One moment, he pretends to be
a meek Fan family live-in son-in-law.

44:26.320 --> 44:28.600
Next moment, he is putting on airs
as Marquis Wu'an.

44:28.680 --> 44:31.160
Now he'll marry the princess
and become imperial consort.

44:31.240 --> 44:32.480
Let me tell you.

44:32.560 --> 44:34.760
If he dares betray our Changyu,

44:35.680 --> 44:38.440
I will… I will…

44:39.080 --> 44:40.120
What can you even do?

44:41.240 --> 44:42.920
I will stay mad at him forever!

47:19.240 --> 47:22.360
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

47:22.840 --> 47:23.680
‎Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
